            idle: ["I've been meaning to reorganize my routes.", "Everything is fine. Fine.", "There's supposed to be a sign here. I've filed a request."],
            hall: ["Two people, both certain. Someone has to rule. Hi.", "Stories crack along the seams. I know where yours are."],
