            provoked: ["Triage protocol: you're last."],
            idle: ["Everyone here looks like they need a checkup.", "Preventative care is always preferable.", "I keep the bandages ready. Just in case."],
            hall: ["Vitals nominal. Mood: untreated. I only do the body, sadly.", "'Walk it off' is not a treatment plan. It is, however, popular."],
        ),
        hall_dialogue_id: Some("hall_npc_robot_medic"),
